text.section:
"Policy" includes:
a policy that is issued to an individual;
a certificate, as that term is used in Title 14, Subtitle 1 of this article, that is issued to an individual subscriber;
a certificate, as that term is used in Title 8, Subtitle 4 of this article, that is issued to a member of a fraternal benefit society; and
a group policy authorized to be issued under this article.
